            <mj-text align="left" font-size="20" color="#4A4A4A" font-weight="700" padding-bottom="0">Inside Our Revolution</mj-text>

            <mj-text align="left" font-size="14" color="#4A4A4A" font-weight="400" padding-top="0">
              <p>Like Bernie Sanders' 2016 Presidential Campaign, Our Revolution runs on a distributed organizing model. This is made possible by volunteers across the country, and the world, working tirelessly for the future they believe in.</p>

              <p>The Our Revolution texting team sends out over 100,000 messages each month - recruiting volunteers, getting out the vote for progressive candidates, and informing people across the country of events that are critical to carrying on the movement. With November elections just around the corner, they could use a few more people willing to spread the word of the political revolution from the comfort of their own homes. Interested? <a href="https://www.textforbernie.com/" target="_blank">Join the Our Revolution texting team now »</a></p>

              <p>Missed the monthly call? <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1aX_QRyznOkVGlQclRYYThrMlU/view" target="_blank">You can still hear a recording of it here »</a>.</p>
            </mj-text>
            
